  7. Delete an application
  </span>
  <div style="display: none; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> The purpose of this feature is to provide GoBabyGo Officers with a simple way to delete unneeded user applications.</p>
    <p><strong>How to Achieve It:</strong> Navigate to the User Applications page (see 1.). Then, select "Delete" next to an application. You will be taken to a new page. To confirm the deletion, select 'Delete Application'. <br/>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

