    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> The purpose of this feature is to provide GoBabyGo Officers with a streamlined way to view all users along with their emails and current role.</p>
    <p><strong>How to Achieve It:</strong> Select -> "Home" -> "Officer Dashboard" -> "View Member Table"</p>
