  9. Change the role of a member
  </span>
  <div style="display: none; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> The purpose of this feature is to provide GoBabyGo Officers with a quick way to update role permissions.</p>
    <p><strong>How to Achieve It:</strong> Navigate to the Member Table page (see 8.). Select the dropdown next to a member email, and then choose the role you want to update that member to. Then, select 'Update Role'.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="margin-bottom: 10px; user-select: none;">
