  10. View/Change your email or phone number.
  </span>
  <div style="display: none; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> The purpose of this feature is to provide GoBabyGo Officers with a quick way to view or update their own contact information.</p>
    <p><strong>How to Achieve It:</strong> Navigate to the Dashboard. Then, select 'Edit Profile'. You will then be presented with your current email and phone contacts.
    To update either, simply directly change the form within the text box, and click update profile once you have made the changes. You will then be routed back to the dashboard.</p>
  </div>
</div>
